WITH t_3_Link AS (SELECT * FROM (

      'b' AS col1 UNION ALL

      'a' AS col0,

) AS UNUSED_TABLE_NAME  ),

      Link.col0 AS col0
    FROM

      t_4_Link.col1 AS col0

) AS UNUSED_TABLE_NAME  ),

FROM

GROUP BY Vertex_MultBodyAggAux.col0),

FROM

GROUP BY PageRank_MultBodyAggAux_recursive_head_f1.col0),
